::GoldenEye::

She glides down to the front of the Pred ship.  She lands and 
transforms into bot mode.  She folds her wings behind her back and 
walks to the door way.  She opens her commlink. "If you can hear me, 
send someone out to greet me. I'm here to join you. If not, then I 
shall be on my way."   She stood there with her hands on her hips.  
She waited for a responce.
